revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yelles}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yelle'' is the 22421<sup>st</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1148 individuals. ''Yelle'' is most common among White (93.55%) individuals.
